    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolutely mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are no scratches, dents, or chips of any kind. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery still firm and the interior trim completely free of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine is whisper-quiet, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and every electronic feature functions exactly as intended. It has been meticulously garage-kept and includes a full service history documenting its pampered life. This is a rare opportunity to own a high-quality vehicle that requires zero investment or attention.",
