      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service record and no issues to report. Buyers can expect a vehicle that drives like new and requires zero additional investment.",
