    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the discerning driver. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a seamless blend of mechanical integrity and refined styling. Every aspect of this automobile has been vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and aesthetic appeal. Experience the perfect balance of longevity and value in a carriage that commands respect on the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
