      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle exemplifies a rigorous standard of maintenance and mechanical integrity. The exterior retains its professional profile, complemented by an interior that demonstrates careful stewardship and consistent upkeep. Engineered for those who demand reliability without compromising on sophistication, this motorcar has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure it meets our exacting benchmarks for performance. This offering represents a premier opportunity to acquire a well-preserved asset at a competitive market valuation.",
      "price": 36800.0,
